Sri Lanka 344-2 at Lunch on Day Three of Second Test Against England

-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 
2011-06-05T12:25:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/sri-lanka-344-2-at-lunch-on-day-three-of-second-test-against-england.html
Sri Lanka  advanced to 344-2 at lunch
on day three of the second cricket Test against  England , 142
runs behind the home team’s first innings total.  Tillakaratne Dilshan  is 187 not out at Lord’s in  London ,
with Mahela Jayawardene on 25. Kumar Sangakkara was the only
batsman dismissed today, edging  Chris Tremlett  to Matt Prior for
26.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 James Cone  at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  